column2: SELECT TOP #  p.run,p.rerun,p.camCol,p.field,p.obj,cast(str(p.ra,#,#) as float) as ra,cast(str(p.[dec],#,#) as float) as dec,p.r,ISNULL(s.spectroFlux_g,#) as spectroFlux_g,ISNULL(s.spectroFlux_i,#) as spectroFlux_i,ISNULL(s.spectroFlux_r,#) as spectroFlux_r,ISNULL(s.spectroFlux_u,#) as spectroFlux_u,ISNULL(s.spectroFlux_z,#) as spectroFlux_z  FROM ..PhotoObj AS p  LEFT OUTER JOIN ..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID  WHERE ( p.type = # OR p.type = #)
